+
+```text
+LeRobot policy
+  -> arm command topic or end-effector target
+  -> arm controller
+  -> simulated arm joints
+
+Task planner or safety bridge
+  -> /uav/target_position or /uav/target_pose
+  -> PX4 Offboard
+  -> stable x500 platform
+```
+
