+- `trajectory_3d.png`
+- `xy_path.png`
+- `height_curve.png`
+- `speed_curve.png`
+- `tracking_error.png`
+- `trajectory.mp4`
+- `summary.md`
+- `result.txt`
+
+Additional Demo 05-specific outputs may include:
+
+- `arm_joints.csv`
+- `end_effector_pose.csv`
+- `contact_events.csv`
+- `contact_result.txt`
